column1: Do you never feel overwhelmed by your workload?
column2: Do you feel your work-life balance is satisfactory?
column3: Do you often feel motivated to complete your tasks at work?
column4: Do you feel comfortable discussing your mental health concerns with your supervisor or colleagues?
column5: Do you never find yourself frequently feeling exhausted or drained at the end of the workday?
column6: Do you never feel pressured to work longer hours or take on additional responsibilities?
column7: Are there any specific resources or programs that your company offers to support employee mental health?
column8: Have you never noticed any changes in your eating or sleeping habits due to work-related stress?
column9: Do you find it easy to relax or unwind after work hours?
column10: Have you never experienced any significant changes in your relationships due to work-related stress?
column11: Have you never felt like giving up or quitting your job?
column12: Do you regularly engage in physical activity or exercise?
column13: Have you never experienced physical symptoms related to anxiety or depression, such as muscle tension, rapid heartbeat, or difficulty breathing?
column14: Have you never experienced any adverse health effects or allergic reactions to food items provided by the company?
